  "text": "To the best of our knowledge, only limited HF, MP2 and DFT calculations of systematic changes in stretch C = C vibrations in C1-C9 [CITATION_1] , as well as C1-C16 [CITATION_2] all-trans polyenes have been reported [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . Furthermore, the characteristic Raman features of all-trans and all-cis polyenes have not been analyzed in detail.",
